OL,3,C'Unprecedented financial challenges':
OL,4,CColeraine theatre to close this summer
OL,6,FThe Riverside Theatre in Coleraine
OL,7,Fwill close this August as it is
OL,8,Fexperiencing "unprecedented financial
OL,9,Fchallenges".
OL,11,FThe venue, based in Ulster
OL,12,FUniversity's campus in the town, has
OL,13,Fbeen in operation for nearly 50 years.
OL,15,FA spokesperson for the university said
OL,16,Fthe building had "come to the end of
OL,17,Fits life and requires significant
OL,18,Fcapital investment to remain in use".
