OL,3,C'Unprecedented financial challenges':
OL,4,CColeraine theatre to close this summer
OL,6,FIt is estimated that this would cost
OL,7,F#745,000 in addition to its annual
OL,8,Frunning costs of #495,000.
OL,10,FThe spokesperson added: "We remain
OL,11,Ffocused on the University's core
OL,12,Fpurpose: to deliver high-quality
OL,13,Fteaching and impactful research across
OL,14,Four multiple campuses.
OL,16,F"And in the face of unprecedented
OL,17,Ffinancial challenges, with the funding
OL,18,Fmodel in Northern Ireland acknowledged
OL,19,Fas unsustainable, it is more important
OL,20,Fthan ever that we focus our resources
OL,21,Fon core academic activities.
